    {"question_text": "What is the output?\n\nclass Middleware:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self._chain = []\n    \n    def use(self, handler):\n        self._chain.append(handler)\n        return self\n    \n    def execute(self, context):\n        def run(index):\n            if index < len(self._chain):\n                return self._chain[index](context, lambda: run(index + 1))\n            return context\n        return run(0)\n\napp = Middleware()\napp.use(lambda ctx, next: {**next(), 'auth': True})\napp.use(lambda ctx, next: {**next(), 'validated': True})\napp.use(lambda ctx, next: {**ctx, 'processed': True})\n\nresult = app.execute({'data': 'test'})\nprint(sorted(result.keys()))", "option_a": "['data', 'processed']", "option_b": "['auth', 'data']", "option_c": "['auth', 'data', 'processed', 'validated']", "option_d": "['data']", "correct_answer": "C", "difficulty": "advanced", "topic": "design_patterns"},
