    {"question_text": "What is the output?\n\nclass Pipeline:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self._steps = []\n        self._error_handler = None\n    \n    def pipe(self, step):\n        self._steps.append(step)\n        return self\n    \n    def on_error(self, handler):\n        self._error_handler = handler\n        return self\n    \n    def execute(self, data):\n        for step in self._steps:\n            try:\n                data = step(data)\n            except Exception as e:\n                if self._error_handler:\n                    return self._error_handler(e, data)\n                raise\n        return data\n\np = Pipeline()\np.pipe(lambda x: x + 1)\np.pipe(lambda x: x * 2)\np.pipe(lambda x: x - 3)\np.on_error(lambda e, d: f'error at {d}')\nresult = p.execute(5)\nprint(result)", "option_a": "14", "option_b": "11", "option_c": "10", "option_d": "9", "correct_answer": "D", "difficulty": "advanced", "topic": "design_patterns"},
