    {"question_text": "What is the output?\n\nclass RuleEngine:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self._rules = []\n    \n    def add_rule(self, condition, action, priority=0):\n        self._rules.append((priority, condition, action))\n        self._rules.sort(key=lambda r: r[0], reverse=True)\n    \n    def evaluate(self, data):\n        for priority, condition, action in self._rules:\n            if condition(data):\n                return action(data)\n        return None\n\nengine = RuleEngine()\nengine.add_rule(lambda d: d > 100, lambda d: 'high', priority=1)\nengine.add_rule(lambda d: d > 50, lambda d: 'medium', priority=2)\nengine.add_rule(lambda d: True, lambda d: 'low', priority=0)\n\nresult = engine.evaluate(75)\nprint(result)", "option_a": "high", "option_b": "low", "option_c": "None", "option_d": "medium", "correct_answer": "D", "difficulty": "advanced", "topic": "design_patterns"},
